Using the large-scale soil databases to indicate local-scale observations introduces uncertainties. To reduce this uncertainty, we compared the SOC density for the available site-depths from the two databases (Supplementary Fig. 5c), and excluded those with a relative difference (calculated as \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
